                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18211024-112-off653 t18211024-112-cd654"></join>, one watch, value 30 s.; one chain, value 2 d.; two keys, value 2 d.; one seal, value 2 d., and one hook, value 2 d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
