                     <interp inst="t18211024-112-person1054" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an apprentice to a pawnbroker, who lives in Duke-street, Manchester-square. On the 24th of October the prisoner pawned the watch.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I intended to redeem it.</p>
